The reason for the infinite recursion is due to the bidirectional relationship between `Form` and `FormSection` entities. When you try to serialize the `Form` entity to return it as a response in the `getFormById` method, it tries to serialize the associated `FormSection` objects. When it serializes the `FormSection` objects, it tries to serialize the associated `Form` objects, which then tries to serialize the associated `FormSection` objects again. This creates an infinite loop, which results in a stack overflow error.

One way to solve this issue is by using a DTO (Data Transfer Object) to return a simplified version of the `Form` entity without the `FormSection` objects. Here's an example of how you could create a DTO for `Form`:
```kotlin
@Data
public class FormDto {
    private Long id;
    private String name;
    private String description;
    private boolean isFinished;
    private List<Long> authorizedAccountIds;

    public FormDto(Form form) {
        this.id = form.getId();
        this.name = form.getName();
        this.description = form.getDescription();
        this.isFinished = form.isFinished();
        this.authorizedAccountIds = form.getAuthorizedAccounts().stream()
                .map(Account::getId)
                .collect(Collectors.toList());
    }
}
```
In this DTO, we're only including the `id`, `name`, `description`, `isFinished` properties, and a list of `authorizedAccountIds`. We're using the `getAuthorizedAccounts` method to get the list of authorized accounts for the `Form` entity and then mapping them to a list of account IDs using the `getId` method.

In the `FormController`, you can use this DTO to return a simplified version of the `Form` entity:
```less
@GetMapping("/{id}")
public ResponseEntity<FormDto> getFormById(@PathVariable Long id){
    Optional<Form> form = formService.getFormById(id);
    return form.map(value -> ResponseEntity.ok(new FormDto(value)))
            .orElseGet(() -> ResponseEntity.notFound().build());
}
```
This way, when the `Form` entity is serialized, it will not include the `FormSection` objects, which will prevent the infinite recursion error.

